cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM 

The paper deals with learning methods for image and video processing tasks, which are typically associated with computer vision (cs.CV). The use of Riemannian geometry and SPD matrices suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The proposed network architecture and backpropagation method are also relevant to neural networks (cs.NE) and multimedia (cs.MM) research.
